I decided to upload this map to FPSbanana after the extreme popularity it recieved on the Geordie-Assassins public server. To play this map, you must set mp_freezetime 0 otherwise you will most likely die. The objective is to avoid the balls, then kill whoever survives. Shooting the glass out above will release more balls, some guns and even a special surprise.

I hope this map brings everyone many days worth of fun on css, both for the serious gamer and casual player.

Other commands for your own personal enjoyment include: phys_timescale X (Changes speed of balls), sv_gravity X changes the gravity.

This is a fun map i created after we did something similar in cs_office. The problem was every on just ran the bots in circles in the open part in the front. So i made this map to remove that and also to make it more difficult to camp when there is no place where you can't get flanked.


Install: Copy the files to the folders needed. The cfg file is a extra added to make it easy.

Use: Type 'exec db_bot' in console. This will change the map and set up the bots for you. If you need to add the bots or more bots type 'exec addbot'. You can add things that need to be turned off beforehand to the turnoff.cfg. I have rpg in it all ready.

Extra: i Suggest having some fun mods and if you have beetles mod i would suggest having RTD on.

Come join us when we play. Add   98.243.109.82:27015   to your favorites and play with us when it's on.

********************
****ctf_castle_wars****
********************
Map made by: Westsid3r & >>Nemesi$[FR]<<

*NEW IN V3*
- Guns can't be spammed.
- Guns protection added, hurt with 25hp when left clicking (same with the knife, dont use it).
- When a flag is saved by his own team, it respawn only if the gun has been removed from the world.
- The player who have the gun is forced to drop it by hurting. (when the flag is saved).
- 1 minutes after the rounds start, the crown can open his own gate.
- Only 1 king per team, if the king die, the crown is destroyed.
- The crowns heal only the players of his own teams.
- The flags are now detected immediatly : dont need to drop it to win.
- Underground added.
- Added more trees, rocks and high grass.
- Fish added in water.
- Water changed.
- Added 12 more spawnpoints.
- Barels respawn 20 seconds after using.
- Barels not kill.
- Lighning changed.
- Cubemap added (= some walls have a reflect).
- Skybox highest.
- Applause can be heared when a team won by taking the flag.
- Flag spawn like a trophy and light spot flashes when a team won with the flag.

Additional settings :

- mp_limitteams 1 (to balance the game)
- mp_freezetime 0 (no need freezetime, no buyzone)

******************
*****Map info:*****
******************

Player spawns: 72 (36 ct, 36 t)
Cannons: 4 (2 on each castle)
The ctf flags are on top of each castle
Players spawn with knife only.

*The flags are attached to a gun (USP)
-Pick it up to take the flag
-Bring it to the second floor in your base and drop it
-If you die, you will drop the gun/flag on the floor. If a person from your team
takes it up, he wields it. If a enemy player takes the flag, the flag will be teleported back to the base.
-If the flag is dropped into water, it will also teleport back to the base.
-There is a gun protection.

*Cannons
-Cannons can shoot after each 5seconds
-There is an instruction manual for the cannons on the wall nearby

*Crowns
-Pick the smokegrenade up above the gate and become the king of your castle
-If you die, crown will be destroyed.
-If you fire the smoke nade, the crown will disappear

*Teamwork
-Is required for more fun
-Knifing the huge doors alone can be hard and boring, easier with more
-Focus on helping the flag holder!

******************

Thanks to:
Zalos for the ctf prefab, which got tweaked by myself.
Smurfii, for his bridge prefab.
Runescape, for the idea.
i3D members and other people that helped testing this map.

I just wanted to see what it would be like if counter strike was mad into a scary single player game. I think that half life 2 is better after putting this together. anyway if you want to try it out, just launch the map with no bots and like normal select which ever team and class you want to be. Then just go ahead and walk through the map. It should probably only take about 30 seconds to finish it. Even though HL2 would be better I still think that this is kinda scary but I know what should happen and when it should happen so I want to know what other people think about it. This will let me know if I am headed in the right direction if I decide to continue this on HL2. So remember leave feedback! Oh and btw you might need to have HL2 installed for the sounds to play in the level, I'm not sure about that though. There should be several sounds throughout the level though.
